<plot>Alieno, a special man, is born. The environment where he evolves and interacts select him as father of future generations. This is the story of a human Alien who observes and reproduces the depth of our daily reality. In the movie two possible interpretations of our time are given and they are presented in this way: the logical and neutral one offered by Alien and the passionate and cruel one of the co-protagonists. The movie deals with the story of a new generation of Italian man, a man of the future. It is not a science fiction movie since it describes the present situation and all the changes that Italians are subjected to, willingly or unwillingly. How will the future Italian be? What will his habits be? What will he think of Italians? How, and above all who, will his friends be?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?030164</url></doc>
